---
import {Icon} from "astro-icon/components";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BlockSection from "../components/BlockSection.astro";
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
---

<Layout
    title="Privacy Policy | AppsByLuke"
    description="This Privacy Policy outlines how AppsByLuke collects, uses, and protects your personal information when using my Services and Website."
>
    <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute top-4 left-6 transform -rotate-2 z-20">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block">
                <Image
                    src='/appsbyluke.svg'
                    width="256.2"
                    loading="eager"
                    height="120"
                    alt="AppsByLuke Logo"
                />
            </a>
        </div>

        <BlockSection id="privacy" backgroundColor="bg-blue-50">
            <div class="mt-32 space-y-8">
                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
                    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how Łukasz Ziaja ("Company," "I," "me," or "my"), operating under
                        the business name AppsByLuke, collects, uses, and protects your information when you use my
                        Services and Website. By using my Services, you agree to the collection and use of information
                        in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Definitions</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">2.1. Company</h3>
                            <p>"Company" refers to Łukasz Ziaja, registered at al. Wiśniowa 36a/304 53-137 Wrocław, Poland,
                                operating under the business name AppsByLuke.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">2.2. Website</h3>
                            <p>"Website" refers to https://appsbyluke.com</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">2.3. Personal Data</h3>
                            <p>Information that can be used to identify you directly or indirectly.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-pink-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">2.4. Usage Data</h3>
                            <p>Information collected automatically through the use of my Services.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Data Collection</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3.1. Personal Data</h3>
                            <p>I may collect:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Name and contact information</li>
                                <li>Business information</li>
                                <li>Payment details</li>
                                <li>Communication preferences</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3.2. Usage Data</h3>
                            <p>I automatically collect:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Browser type and version</li>
                                <li>Access times and dates</li>
                                <li>Pages viewed</li>
                                <li>Device information</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3.3. Analytics</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Self-hosted Plausible Analytics (cookie-free analytics solution)</li>
                                <li>No personal data collection for analytics purposes</li>
                                <li>No cookies used for tracking</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-pink-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3.4. Third-Party Service Providers</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Monitor and analyze website usage</li>
                                <li>Process payments</li>
                                <li>Provide hosting services</li>
                                <li>Send communications</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3.5. Data Collection Purposes</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>To provide and maintain my Services</li>
                                <li>To notify you about changes to my Services</li>
                                <li>To provide customer support</li>
                                <li>To gather analysis for improving my Services</li>
                                <li>To monitor usage of my Services</li>
                                <li>To detect, prevent and address technical issues</li>
                                <li>To fulfill legal obligations</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-orange-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3.6. Legal Requirements</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
                                <li>To protect and defend my rights or property</li>
                                <li>To prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing</li>
                                <li>To protect against legal liability</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Data Processing</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4.1. Data Processing Location</h3>
                            <p>Your information is processed at my operating offices and in any other places where the
                                parties involved in the processing are located. This means that your data may be transferred
                                to — and maintained on — computers located outside of your state, province, country, or
                                other governmental jurisdiction.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4.2. Data Processing Consent</h3>
                            <p>Your consent to this Privacy Policy followed by your submission of personal information
                                represents your agreement to such transfer.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4.3. Data Processing Security</h3>
                            <p>I take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure that your data is treated securely and in
                                accordance with this Privacy Policy. No transfer of your Personal Data will take place to an
                                organization or a country unless there are adequate controls in place.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Data Protection</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">5.1. Security Measures</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Implementation of industry-standard security protocols</li>
                                <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
                                <li>Secure data encryption in transit and at rest</li>
                                <li>Access controls and authentication measures</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">5.2. Data Breaches</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Prompt notification of any security breaches</li>
                                <li>Investigation and mitigation procedures</li>
                                <li>Cooperation with relevant authorities</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">5.3. International Data Transfers</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>All international transfers comply with GDPR requirements</li>
                                <li>Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) are implemented where necessary</li>
                                <li>Appropriate safeguards are in place for data transfers outside the EEA</li>
                                <li>Transparency about data storage locations and transfer mechanisms</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Data Storage and Transfer</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">6.1. Storage Location</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Data stored both within and outside the European Economic Area (EEA)</li>
                                <li>Use of international service providers including:
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-8 mt-2">
                                        <li>Cloudflare (USA)</li>
                                        <li>Other US-based cloud service providers</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li>International transfers protected by appropriate safeguards:
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-8 mt-2">
                                        <li>Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs)</li>
                                        <li>Service providers' compliance with EU-US Data Privacy Framework</li>
                                        <li>Additional technical and organizational measures</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">6.2. Retention Period</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Data retained only as long as necessary</li>
                                <li>Analytics data retained for 14 months</li>
                                <li>Regular review of stored information</li>
                                <li>Secure deletion of unnecessary data</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <p>Under GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Right to access your personal data</li>
                                <li>Right to rectification of inaccurate data</li>
                                <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
                                <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
                                <li>Right to data portability</li>
                                <li>Right to object to processing</li>
                                <li>Right to withdraw consent</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">8.1. Types of Cookies Used</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Essential cookies for website functionality only</li>
                                <li>No tracking or analytics cookies used</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">8.2. Analytics</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Self-hosted Plausible Analytics for basic website statistics</li>
                                <li>No personal data collection</li>
                                <li>No cookies required for analytics</li>
                                <li>Compliant with GDPR and privacy regulations</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">8.3. Third-Party Services</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Payment processors for transactions</li>
                                <li>Hosting and infrastructure providers</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <p>My Services are not intended for use by children under 18 years of age. I do not knowingly
                                collect personal information from children. If you become aware that a child has provided me
                                with personal information, please contact me.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">10. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Right to update this policy at any time</li>
                                <li>Notification of material changes via email</li>
                                <li>30 days notice for significant changes</li>
                                <li>Continued use constitutes acceptance</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">11. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">11.1. I process your data based on:</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Contract performance</li>
                                <li>Legal obligations</li>
                                <li>Legitimate interests</li>
                                <li>Your consent</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">11.2. Legitimate Interests Include:</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Improving my Services</li>
                                <li>Security and fraud prevention</li>
                                <li>Business administration</li>
                                <li>Marketing (where permitted)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">12. Contact Information</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <p class="mb-4">For any questions about this Privacy Policy or my data practices:</p>
                            <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                                <li>Data Controller: Łukasz Ziaja</li>
                                <li>Operating as: AppsByLuke</li>
                                <li>Address: al. Wiśniowa 36a/304</li>
                                <li>53-137 Wrocław</li>
                                <li>Poland</li>
                                <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@appsbyluke.com"
                                              class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">privacy@appsbyluke.com</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Response Times for Data Requests</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                                <li>Access requests: Within 30 days</li>
                                <li>Deletion requests: Within 30 days</li>
                                <li>Data portability requests: Within 30 days</li>
                                <li>Privacy concerns: Within 5 business days</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-black p-4">
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Supervisory Authority</h3>
                            <p class="mb-4">You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. For
                                Poland, the supervisory authority is:</p>
                            <ul class="list-none space-y-2">
                                <li>President of the Personal Data Protection Office (UODO)</li>
                                <li>ul. Stawki 2, 00-193 Warsaw</li>
                                <li>Poland</li>
                                <li>Website: <a href="https://uodo.gov.pl/"
                                                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">https://uodo.gov.pl/</a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t-2 border-black">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
                        <p class="text-sm mb-2 md:mb-0">
                            Last Updated: February 20, 2025
                            <a href="https://github.com/logical-luke/appsbyluke/commits/main/landing/src/pages/privacy-policy.astro"
                               class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline ml-2"
                               target="_blank"
                               rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                (Version History)
                            </a>
                        </p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <Icon name="tabler:shield-lock" class="w-5 h-5"/>
                            <span class="text-sm font-bold">Official Privacy Policy Document</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </BlockSection>
    </div>
</Layout>
